    <Label name="lblDescription" id="0322dc96-79a6-4bad-b600-c4a061323a1b">
        <alignment>1</alignment>
        <caption>To add a selection criteria, click the 'New' button, choose the 'Include' or 'Exclude' option, select the property and the operand, enter the value (do not enclose values in quotes), then click the 'Add' button.

To edit a criteria, select it, make the changes, then click the 'Update' button.  To remove a criteria, select it, then click the 'Remove' button.  To remove all selection criteria, click the 'Clear All' button.

Click the 'OK' button to apply the selection criteria to the list of objects, or click the 'Cancel' button.</caption>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>8421440</foreColor>
        <parent name="CnEcObjectFilterForm"/>
        <parentBottomOffset>304</parentBottomOffset>
        <parentRightOffset>10</parentRightOffset>
